cz.cvut.felk.cig.jcop.problem
Interface ObjectiveProblem

All Superinterfaces:
DestinationProblem, GlobalSearchProblem, Problem, RandomConfigurationProblem, StartingConfigurationProblem
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseObjectiveProblem
public interface ObjectiveProblem
extends StartingConfigurationProblem, RandomConfigurationProblem, DestinationProblem, Problem, GlobalSearchProblem

Objective problem groups all problem interfaces into one and adds methods to determine if an implementation has these interfaces really implemented or just they throw an exception if interface's method is called.

See Also:
BaseObjectiveProblem is basic implementation of ObjectiveProblem interface and should be base class for all problems (or at least all local search problems).
